WEBVTT

00:00:06.323 --> 00:00:10.912
=The Ascent of Ling Yun=

00:00:11.059 --> 00:00:13.312
=Episode 21=

00:00:13.427 --> 00:00:15.776
(Consort Wan's Blood Bath
Exposed and Witnessed!)

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:27.080
That vile witch Zhao Yanwan.

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:29.040
Her audacity grows beyond measure!

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:30.816
Noble Lady Zhao,

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:32.200
I entrust

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:33.880
the next act to you.

00:00:35.360 --> 00:00:37.240
I will make everyone witness

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:38.840
Zhao Yanwan's wretched

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:40.880
half-human, half-ghost appearance.

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:44.080
I'll utterly ruin her reputation

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:45.720
and make her life miserable.

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:00.480
You've been following me.

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:02.016
Show yourself.

00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:11.776
What do you need?

00:01:13.160 --> 00:01:14.600
How come you left Chengxi Palace?

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.480
Your eyes deceived you.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.024
What's with your hand?

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:22.560
Nothing.

00:01:31.320 --> 00:01:32.760
You're His Majesty's Noble Lady now.

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:34.680
Consort Wan dared touch you?

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:37.560
I provoked it.

00:01:38.320 --> 00:01:39.920
To expose Consort Wan's true nature,

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:41.360
I don't care

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:42.960
how great the cost is.

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:43.936
But I do.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:01:58.360
Your Highness.

00:01:59.080 --> 00:01:59.960
Have you decided?

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:03.200
From now on,

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:04.920
I am

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:06.040
at Your Highness's command.

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:08.720
Is Ling Yun really

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:10.720
so important to you?

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:12.720
If her safety and escape

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:13.920
can be assured,

00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:15.648
I will

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:17.120
endure ten thousand deaths.

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.144
Well then.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.280
Attendant Cheng
of Shangyun Pavilion is pregnant.

00:02:22.160 --> 00:02:23.360
She's been hiding it.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:26.560
Since she wants the child
to remain unseen,

00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:31.320
help make it disappear.

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:33.696
Your Highness,

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:35.800
it's an imperial heir.

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:38.000
It's merely an unformed fetus.

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.320
Didn't you swear
to endure ten thousand deaths?

00:02:42.320 --> 00:02:43.232
What?

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:44.920
Do you recant so quickly?

00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:49.280
Your Highness is right.

00:02:49.824 --> 00:02:50.720
I

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:51.872
shall see it done.

00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:13.888
Tong An,

00:03:15.600 --> 00:03:18.040
have an abortifacient
brought from outside the palace.

00:03:19.320 --> 00:03:20.224
Master,

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.720
will you help Consort Jing?

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:24.512
But Master,

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:25.520
if you take this step,

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:26.840
there'll be no turning back.

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.920
Why does Consort Jing
compel you to do it?

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.320
Prepare the medicine for me.

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:32.128
From now on,

00:03:32.360 --> 00:03:34.000
serve diligently in the Imperial Study.

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:36.128
Avoid

00:03:37.400 --> 00:03:38.720
all further contact with me.

00:03:54.740 --> 00:03:56.740
Consort Wan's temperament
has drastically changed,

00:03:57.020 --> 00:03:57.940
with wild mood swings,

00:03:58.220 --> 00:03:59.820
as if possessed by some spirit.

00:03:59.940 --> 00:04:00.980
I've heard it.

00:04:00.980 --> 00:04:02.060
It's throughout the palace.

00:04:02.540 --> 00:04:03.620
Surely it cannot be true?

00:04:03.980 --> 00:04:06.620
Now all avoid Chengxi Palace's vicinity.

00:04:07.300 --> 00:04:09.740
Those serving Consort Wan are suffering,

00:04:10.140 --> 00:04:11.700
enduring her daily beatings and abuse,

00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:14.340
with no end in sight.

00:04:15.340 --> 00:04:16.620
We must exercise caution

00:04:16.940 --> 00:04:18.020
to avoid trouble.

00:04:18.340 --> 00:04:19.300
Indeed.

00:04:21.940 --> 00:04:24.140
Your Majesty appears weary.

00:04:25.140 --> 00:04:26.780
Does some matter trouble you?

00:04:28.140 --> 00:04:30.140
Court affairs bring endless turbulence,

00:04:31.020 --> 00:04:31.940
while the harem

00:04:32.620 --> 00:04:33.740
grants me no peace either.

00:04:36.620 --> 00:04:37.580
Has Your Majesty

00:04:38.420 --> 00:04:39.860
heard any rumors?

00:04:43.180 --> 00:04:45.900
Recent palace gossip
concerns Consort Wan

00:04:46.540 --> 00:04:47.700
with unclear veracity.

00:04:48.140 --> 00:04:49.540
Should Your Majesty find time,

00:04:49.700 --> 00:04:51.540
visit Chengxi Palace more often.

00:04:52.140 --> 00:04:53.300
You've heard it too?

00:04:53.300 --> 00:04:54.244
Yes.

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:56.980
I trust Your Majesty
has already considered

00:04:57.340 --> 00:04:58.420
and hesitated to speak.

00:04:59.380 --> 00:05:00.940
But my concern compels me.

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:03.900
If Consort Wan's condition persists,

00:05:04.220 --> 00:05:05.740
the rumors will intensify,

00:05:06.740 --> 00:05:08.340
threatening imperial dignity.

00:05:09.140 --> 00:05:10.180
You're right.

00:05:10.980 --> 00:05:12.340
I shall address Consort Wan's

00:05:12.420 --> 00:05:13.420
mental affliction.

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:15.180
Tong An,

00:05:15.180 --> 00:05:16.260
pass down the order.

00:05:16.340 --> 00:05:18.140
I shall dine at Chengxi Palace tonight.

00:05:18.836 --> 00:05:19.808
Yes.

00:05:20.500 --> 00:05:21.580
His Majesty is coming?

00:05:21.580 --> 00:05:24.100
His Majesty just sent a message,

00:05:24.140 --> 00:05:26.100
saying that he will have dinner here.

00:05:27.580 --> 00:05:28.940
How do I look now?

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:31.340
Your Highness's
divine beauty and splendor

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:32.620
is unmatched.

00:05:34.380 --> 00:05:35.296
No.

00:05:37.980 --> 00:05:39.740
I look too haggard.

00:05:43.100 --> 00:05:44.900
His Majesty will surely dislike me.

00:05:47.940 --> 00:05:48.832
Where is Ling Zhu?

00:05:49.980 --> 00:05:51.008
I want to bathe.

00:05:51.220 --> 00:05:52.256
I want to bathe.

00:05:52.700 --> 00:05:53.660
Summon Ling Zhu.

00:05:57.651 --> 00:05:58.752
I want to bathe.

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:00.960
I want to bathe.

00:06:01.940 --> 00:06:03.552
(Yongxiu Palace)

00:06:06.432 --> 00:06:07.380
Your Ladyship,

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:08.340
Ling Zhu sent word.

00:06:08.740 --> 00:06:11.380
Consort Wan heard His Majesty
would dine at Chengxi Palace.

00:06:11.700 --> 00:06:12.620
She wants a blood bath.

00:06:14.780 --> 00:06:15.940
The show

00:06:16.540 --> 00:06:18.260
is about to begin at last.

00:07:33.740 --> 00:07:35.140
What's happening outside?

00:07:36.180 --> 00:07:37.140
Your Highness,

00:07:37.140 --> 00:07:38.900
I tripped by accident.

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:53.040
(My dear sister,)

00:07:53.240 --> 00:07:56.320
(I had Shun Xi add numbing herbs)

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:58.440
(to your usual incense tonight.)

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:01.480
(The effect should be taking hold now.)

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:12.384
Your Ladyship,

00:08:12.384 --> 00:08:14.234
Consort Jing, Concubine Shu,
Noble Lady Rong,

00:08:14.234 --> 00:08:15.904
Attendant Li, Attendant Cheng,
and others

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.480
are all heading to Chengxi Palace.

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:19.456
Good.

00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:21.080
Let's depart too

00:08:21.280 --> 00:08:22.840
to witness the spectacle.

00:08:38.496 --> 00:08:41.152
His Majesty and I
share profound affection.

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:44.576
Once I finish bathing

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:46.080
and adorn myself meticulously,

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:49.120
I shall radiate magnificence.

00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:52.780
When His Majesty
beholds my peerless beauty,

00:08:53.660 --> 00:08:55.140
his heart shall surely sway,

00:08:55.900 --> 00:08:58.180
and I will regain his exclusive favor.

00:09:12.820 --> 00:09:14.500
What... what is this?

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.340
I've no idea.

00:09:16.740 --> 00:09:17.860
Who is that?

00:09:19.500 --> 00:09:20.436
Consort Jing.

00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:26.500
Is this a performance
arranged by some palace?

00:09:27.060 --> 00:09:27.980
Concubine Shu,

00:09:28.260 --> 00:09:30.848
does that appear to be someone
bathing behind the curtains?

00:09:30.899 --> 00:09:31.840
I don't know.

00:09:32.660 --> 00:09:35.380
Who would bathe in public like this?

00:09:35.620 --> 00:09:36.940
It's so bizarre.

00:09:37.140 --> 00:09:39.420
I've never seen such a method
to vie for favor.

00:09:42.004 --> 00:09:43.232
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

00:09:44.500 --> 00:09:45.683
Your Majesty.

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.504
What kind of act is this?

00:09:50.260 --> 00:09:51.460
Your Majesty,

00:09:51.460 --> 00:09:52.500
I have no idea.

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:55.380
I heard of a strange occurrence
in the palace

00:09:55.620 --> 00:09:56.700
drawing crowds to witness.

00:09:57.140 --> 00:09:58.020
So I came to observe.

00:10:05.020 --> 00:10:05.876
It's Consort Wan.

00:10:05.876 --> 00:10:06.900
What?

00:10:06.900 --> 00:10:08.340
- Consort Wan?
- It's Consort Wan?

00:10:08.460 --> 00:10:09.940
What exactly is she doing?

00:10:10.388 --> 00:10:11.340
Your Majesty,

00:10:11.340 --> 00:10:15.580
recent palace rumors
suggest Consort Wan's instability.

00:10:16.060 --> 00:10:17.660
I initially dismissed them,

00:10:18.020 --> 00:10:20.740
but now it seems like
they weren't unfounded.

00:10:21.100 --> 00:10:24.620
I shall discover
what trickery she is performing.

00:10:49.300 --> 00:10:51.300
- It's Consort Wan.
- Yes, it's her.

00:10:51.300 --> 00:10:52.340
Why is she bathing here?

00:10:52.340 --> 00:10:53.220
Why am I here?

00:10:57.696 --> 00:10:59.680
- Your Majesty.
- Has she gone mad?

00:10:59.820 --> 00:11:00.992
- Your Majesty!
- Exactly.

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:03.155
Your Majesty!

00:11:03.252 --> 00:11:04.276
It's not what it seems!

00:11:04.340 --> 00:11:05.500
Let me explain, Your Majesty!

00:11:05.860 --> 00:11:07.020
Hear me, Your Majesty!

00:11:07.460 --> 00:11:08.300
It isn't true!

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:10.260
It's not what it seems!

00:11:10.660 --> 00:11:11.508
Guards!

00:11:11.780 --> 00:11:12.900
Take her back to her palace.

00:11:13.580 --> 00:11:14.620
Regarding today's event,

00:11:14.620 --> 00:11:15.636
should word spread,

00:11:16.220 --> 00:11:17.236
execution awaits!